                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "data": "The `npm install` succeeded — that's all you need. The audit fix error is a separate issue from running a half-installed `node_modules` left over from the Windows attempt conflicting with the rename. Don't worry about it.\n\nJust clean up and reinstall cleanly:\n\n```bash\nrm -rf node_modules\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\nThat will give you a clean install from WSL with no leftover Windows artifacts, and then start the dev server."
                  }
