                "role": "assistant",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "data": "Zero errors. Done. Here's a summary of everything implemented:\n\n---\n\n## What was added / changed\n\n### New files\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `src/topologies.ts` | 6 generator functions, one per topology |\n| `src/topologyMeta.ts` | `TOPOLOGIES` array — name, description, 12+ feature rows per topology |\n| `src/TopologySelector.ts` | Left sidebar with one button per topology |\n| `src/TopologyInfo.ts` | Right panel with description + features table |\n\n### Updated files\n| File | Change |\n|---|---|\n| `src/NetworkGraph.ts` | Added `clear()` method that disposes all nodes/links from scene |\n| `src/main.ts` | Completely rewired to use selector + info panel; `loadTopology()` clears and rebuilds on demand |\n| `index.html` | Added `#topology-selector` nav and `#topology-info` aside |\n| `src/style.css` | Full dark-theme layout with sidebar, info panel, features table, scrollbars |\n\n### Topologies implemented (from the PDF)\n\n| Topology | Geometry | Key feature |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Malla** | 4×4 grid of switches | DOR XY routing, non-symmetric |\n| **Toroide** | 4×4 + wrap-around links | Symmetric, homogeneous, better bisection BW |\n| **WK-Recursiva** | 4 groups of 4 cliques | Recursive structure, high connectivity |\n| **Fat Tree** | Binary tree (k=2, n=4) | Grows wider at root, up/down routing |\n| **Flattened Butterfly** | 4×4 all-to-all rows+cols | Low hop count, high switch degree |\n| **Bus** | Star around central bus node | Simplest, single point of failure |\n\nTo run (from WSL terminal):\n```bash\ncd ~/Simulador_topologia_red/network-topology\nnpm run dev\n```"
                  }
                ],
                "meta": {
