                "role": "assistant",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "data": "Done. Here's a summary of what was added to the README:\n\n- **Features** — three new bullets covering 3D tube links, arced torus wrap-around links, and arced/color-coded butterfly links.\n- **Torus section** — added a note explaining the arc and per-dimension color scheme (red / violet / teal / amber).\n- **Flattened Butterfly section** — added a note explaining row links (amber, arc up) vs. column links (violet, arc forward).\n- **Project Structure** — updated `NetworkLink.ts` description to mention tube geometry, arc support, and per-link color override.\n- **Architecture Overview** — updated `NetworkLink` entry to describe `TubeGeometry` + `MeshPhongMaterial` + `CatmullRom` curve; added `buildGraph` note about forwarding `arc`/`color`; added a new **Link rendering** subsection with a table documenting the `arc` and `color` fields and which topologies use them.\n- **Troubleshooting** — updated the FPS row to mention Flattened Butterfly tube count growth."
                  }
                ],
                "meta": {
                  "timestamp": 1783334294
                }
              }
            },
