            "data": "The issue is clear: the shell Kiro CLI is using is the Windows Node.js/npm, which can't install into a WSL path from a UNC route. This is an environment constraint — `npm install` must be run from a WSL terminal. The project files are correct. Let me document this in the README so the steps are crystal clear:"
