            "data": "I have all the content from the PDF. Now I have a clear picture of the topologies covered:\n\n1. **Mesh (Malla)** — k-ary n-mesh, 2D mesh, hypercube\n2. **Torus (Toroide)** — k-ary n-cube, folded torus\n3. **WK-Recursive**\n4. **Fat Tree** — k-ary n-tree\n5. **Flattened Butterfly**\n6. **Shared Medium / Bus** (mentioned as simplest shared-medium network)\n\nLet me now plan and implement everything:"
          },
