          {
            "kind": "text",
            "data": "Good — I have a clear picture of all four files. The plan:\n\n1. **`topologyMeta.ts`** — replace static `features` arrays and `generate()` with a `params` definition (field name, label, type, constraints) and a `computeFeatures(params)` + `generate(params)` that recalculate everything from the live values.\n2. **`TopologyInfo.ts`** — add a parameter form above the features table; on change, recompute features and re-render the graph.\n3. **`topologies.ts`** — make all generators accept a typed params object.\n4. **`main.ts`** — thread the params through `loadTopology`.\n5. **`style.css`** — style the param form."
          },
